HOW TO COOK MALA XIANG GUO 麻辣香锅 - SWIPE LEFT

MLXG is a feisty and super addictive dish that many Singaporeans love! This is my simple recipe for beginners.

It is quite easy to cook this sumptuous dish at home - the only downside is that I had to spent quite a bit of time on preparing the ingredients. More details via link in bio.
